sentence:
Original sentence: "Scott Sheldrick, who graduated in Molecular Genetics, won the Europe award for Life Sciences, Chester Cornford studied MSc Mental Health Nursing and was awarded the Nursing, Midwifery & Allied Healthcare prize, whilst Lola Knibb won the Visual Arts award." 
 Translated sentence: "斯科特·谢尔德里克(英语:Scott Sheldrick)毕业于分子遗传学,获得了欧洲生命科学奖,切斯特·康福德(英语:Chester Cornford)学习了MSc精神健康护理,并获得了护理、助产和联合医疗保健奖,而洛拉·克尼布(英语:Lola Knibb)则获得了视觉艺术奖。"

Original sentence: "A Florida man has pleaded guilty to kidnapping a plastic surgeon who was tortured with a blowtorch in an extortion attempt." 
 Translated sentence: "佛 罗 里 达 州 一 名 男 子 承 认 绑 架 了 一 名 整 形 外 科 医 生 ， 该 外 科 医 生 在 勒 索 企 图 中 被 喷 枪 折 磨 。"

Original sentence: "The book was co-written with T. Shawn Taylor, journalist, writer and founder of Tree Top Consulting, a full-service media consulting firm." 
 Translated sentence: "这 本 书 是 与 T . Shawn Taylor 共 同 撰 写 的 ， T . Shawn Taylor 是 一 位 记 者 、 作 家 ， 也 是 一 家 全 服 务 媒 体 咨 询 公 司 Tree Top Consulting 的 创 始 人 。"

Original sentence: "The sentencing phase is expected to last around 2 ½ weeks, the station reported." 
 Translated sentence: "据电视台报道，判决阶段预计将持续约两周半。"

Original sentence: "Clinic directors previously testified the wait period causes women financial hardship and stress. They also said the two-visit requirement poses logistical challenges for patients and clinics that cause abortions to be delayed far beyond the 48 hours required by law, pushing some women into surgical abortions, which have greater risks of complications. A few women are pushed beyond the time when they can receive an abortion altogether." 
 Translated sentence: "诊所主任以前曾作证说,等候期给妇女造成经济困难和压力,他们还说,两访要求给病人和诊所造成后勤困难,导致堕胎延误远远超过法律规定的48小时,迫使一些妇女接受外科手术堕胎,并发症的风险更大,一些妇女被推到可以完全接受堕胎的时间之后。"

Original sentence: "Defense Secretary Mark Esper has "approved putting additional forces on prepare to deploy orders," Pentagon spokesman Jonathan Hoffman wrote in a statement. "While no decision has been made to deploy these additional forces, they will maintain a heightened state of readiness."" 
 Translated sentence: "五角大楼发言人乔纳森·霍夫曼在一份声明中写道，国防部长马克·埃斯珀已经“批准增派部队准备部署命令，”虽然还没有决定部署这些增派部队，但他们将保持高度戒备状态。“"

Original sentence: "The man arrived at work about 9.30am after failing to reply to several text messages and phone calls from colleagues." 
 Translated sentence: "这名男子上午9时30分左右到达工作地点，此前他没有回复同事的几条短信和电话。"

Original sentence: "But the austere kingdom, which forbids alcohol and has a strict social code, is seen by many as a hard sell for tourists." 
 Translated sentence: "但严峻的王国，禁止酒精和有严格的社会代码，被许多人视为游客的硬销。"

Original sentence: "Failing to get the funding he desired for borders on the southern border from both the Mexican government and Congress, Trump declared the national emergency in February. His administration plans to pull $3.6 billion from military construction to fund border projects." 
 Translated sentence: "特朗普未能从墨西哥政府和国会获得他希望的南部边境边境资金，于2月份宣布全国进入紧急状态。他的政府计划从军事建设中拿出36亿美元来资助边境项目。"

Original sentence: "Ericksen was removed from the priesthood in 1988." 
 Translated sentence: "1988年,埃里克森被辞去了牧师职务。"

Original sentence: "A former priest accused of sexually assaulting young boys in Wisconsin decades ago has been sentenced to 30 years in prison." 
 Translated sentence: "几十年前, 一位被控在威斯康星州性侵犯年轻男孩的前牧师被判入狱30年."

Original sentence: "Serena Williams Fined $10,000 For Allegedly Damaging Wimbledon Court" 
 Translated sentence: "塞雷娜*威廉姆斯因涉嫌破坏温布尔登球场而被罚款1万美元"

Original sentence: "Thursday marks the International Day for the Total Elimination of Nuclear Weapons, but it's a goal that looks increasingly less likely." 
 Translated sentence: "星期四是彻底消除核武器国际日，但这一目标似乎越来越不可能实现。"

Original sentence: "As for the growth in investments, there are no surprises there, either. The bulk of these has been made in the United States and Canada." 
 Translated sentence: "至于投资的增长，也没有什么意外。其中大部分是在美国和加拿大制造的。"

Original sentence: "In the 1950s and '60s as scientists began to obtain high resolution images of viruses, they discovered the detailed structure of the capsid -- an outer protective layer composed of multiple copies of the same protein -- which protects the virus' genetic material. The majority of viruses have capsids that are typically quasi-spherical and display icosahedral symmetry -- like a 20-sided dice for instance." 
 Translated sentence: "在20世纪50年代和60年代，当科学家开始获得病毒的高分辨率图像时，他们发现了衣壳的详细结构-一个由同一蛋白质的多个拷贝组成的外部保护层-它保护病毒的遗传物质。大多数病毒的衣壳通常是准球形的，并显示出二十面体的对称性，例如20面骰子。"

Original sentence: ""I think he took it as best as you could expect," said Doug Durham, one of Haskell's defense attorneys, according to the station. "He was aware that this was a strong possibility."" 
 Translated sentence: "据 本 台 报 道 ， 哈 斯 卡 尔 的 辩 护 律 师 之 一 道 格 · 杜 伦 说 ： “ 我 认 为 他 已 经 尽 了 你 所 能 ， 他 意 识 到 这 种 可 能 性 很 大 。 ”"

Original sentence: "The consultation runs until January 15 and contains proposals to toughen and clarify the current legislation, including questioning whether a national dog control database should be created." 
 Translated sentence: "咨询将持续到1月15日，其中提出了加强和澄清现行立法的建议，包括质疑是否应建立国家狗控制数据库。"

Original sentence: "How does national governance adapt to the changing world?" 
 Translated sentence: "国家治理如何适应不断变化的世界?"

Original sentence: "He is now in Belmarsh prison in London after being jailed for violating bail conditions imposed over the Swedish extradition request and was due to be released last week, but was remanded in custody pending a hearing of the US extradition case in London in February 2020." 
 Translated sentence: "他因违反瑞典引渡请求规定的保释条件而被监禁，原定于上周获释，目前被关押在伦敦的贝尔马什监狱，但被还押候审，等待2020年2月在伦敦举行的美国引渡案听证会。"

Original sentence: "Prolonged monsoon brings floods and chaos to many parts of India" 
 Translated sentence: "长时间的季风给印度许多地方带来洪灾和混乱"

Original sentence: "However, he decided to take a polygraph test to dispel any speculation that he was the one who sent the tweet to himself, his lawyer Megan Kiefer, said. A lawsuit has not yet been filed on Dunlap's behalf, but he said in his statement that one would be coming, according to WWL-TV." 
 Translated sentence: "然而，他的律师梅根·基弗（ Megan Kiefer ）说，他决定接受测谎仪测试，以消除任何关于他是向自己发送推文的人的猜测。"

Original sentence: "Since the 1960s, these viral capsids have been classified using the geometrical framework introduced by structural biologist Donald Caspar and biophysicist Aaron Klug, which were inspired by the geodesic domes designed by the renowned architect R. Buckminster Fuller. However, as molecular imaging techniques have advanced, an increasing number of 3D viral capsid reconstructions that included viruses like Herpes or Zika have fallen out from this classical geometrical framework." 
 Translated sentence: "自 20 世纪 60 年代以来 ， 这些病毒的捕获物被用结构生物学家 Donald Caspar 和生物物理学家 Aaron Klug 引入的几何框架进行了分类 ， 这些几何框架是由著名建筑师 R. BuckcasterFuller 设计的 ， 但随着分子成像技术的进步 ， 越来越多的 3D 病毒结构被包括在内 ， 这类病毒已经从经典的基因图谱中消失。"

Original sentence: "Visas in the desert kingdom, endowed with rich bedouin heritage and archaeological sites, are currently restricted to expat workers, their dependents and Muslim pilgrims travelling to holy sites in Mecca and Medina." 
 Translated sentence: "沙漠王国拥有丰富的贝都因人遗产和考古遗址的签证目前仅限于前往麦加和麦地那圣地的外籍工人及其家属和穆斯林朝圣者。"

Original sentence: "The IAAF, the global governing body of athletics, said the women's marathon, scheduled to start at midnight on Friday, would go ahead as planned as temperatures would be at or below 30 degrees." 
 Translated sentence: "田径联合会是全球田径理事会,它说定于星期五午夜开始的妇女马拉松赛将按计划进行,因为气温将达到或低于30度。"

Original sentence: "The agreement also allows Spidey to appear in a future Marvel Studios film." 
 Translated sentence: "该协议还允许 Spidey 出现在未来的 Marvel Stordios 电影中。"

Original sentence: "Speaking to mother-of-two Lara Rosmarin, CEO of Cape Innovation and Technology, Meghan said: 'We're only five months in right now. Being a working mum and travelling as well with a baby, my goodness it's a lot, but it's all so exciting." 
 Translated sentence: "梅根在接受开普创新科技公司( Cape Innovation and Technology )首席执行官劳拉?罗斯马林( Lara Rosmarin )的采访时说：“我们现在只有5个月的时间，作为一个工作妈妈，带着孩子旅行，我的天哪，这很多，但这一切都太令人兴奋了。"

Original sentence: ""The European tobacco products directive restricts the advertising of e-cigarettes and ensures that e-liquids cannot contain ingredients that are known to be harmful." 
 Translated sentence: "“欧洲烟草制品指令限制了电子烟的广告投放，并确保电子烟油不能包含已知有害的成分。"

Original sentence: "LNG investments hit record in 2019 & the biggest growth is coming from China" 
 Translated sentence: "LNG投资在2019年创历史新高，最大增长来自中国"

Original sentence: "Thousands of people staged a peaceful protest at a downtown square Friday night against alleged abuse of power by police, waving anti-police banners and chanting pro-democracy slogans. The government has said complaints against police will be examined by a police watchdog agency that critics say is toothless and has no real investigative powers." 
 Translated sentence: "上周五晚间，数千人在市中心广场举行和平抗议活动，抗议警方滥用权力，他们挥舞着反警察标语，高呼支持民主的口号。政府表示，对警方的投诉将由一个警察监督机构进行审查，批评者认为该机构没有效力，也没有真正的调查权力。"

Original sentence: "When she pleaded "stop, stop, stop," he put her in a headlock and forced her into the scrub." 
 Translated sentence: "当她恳求"停止，停止，停止"，他把她锁在头锁，并强迫她到磨砂。"

Original sentence: "In the final series, Rachel's onscreen husband Mike Ross, played by Patrick J Adams, paid a visit from Seattle and was asked how Rachel was getting on." 
 Translated sentence: "在最后的系列中，由帕特里克· J ·亚当斯扮演的瑞秋在银幕上的丈夫迈克·罗斯从西雅图拜访，并被问及瑞秋的表现如何。"

Original sentence: "A Spanish private security company hired to protect the Ecuadorian embassy in London when Julian Assange lived there spied on the WikiLeaks founder for the US intelligence service, it has been claimed." 
 Translated sentence: "有人声称，朱利安·阿桑奇（Julian Assange）居住在伦敦的厄瓜多尔一家西班牙私人安全公司在美国情报机构WikiLeaks创始人的间谍下住在那里，以保护伦敦的厄瓜多尔大使馆。"

Original sentence: "A Harris County jury found Ronald Haskell, 39, guilty in the July 2014 killings of six members of the Stay family: parents Stephen Stay and Katie Stay, and children Bryan, 13, Emily, 9, Rebecca, 7 and Zach, 4." 
 Translated sentence: "哈里斯县陪审团认定，39岁的罗纳德·哈斯克尔在2014年7月杀害了“留下”家族的6名成员：父母斯蒂芬·留下和凯蒂·留下，以及13岁的孩子布莱恩、9岁的艾米莉、7岁的丽贝卡和4岁的扎克。"

Original sentence: ""Our daughters thought [Warren] was nice," Dan Michels, a Trump supporter and a father to one of the girls, told the Washington Free Beacon. "She came by and told us we should vote for her. And our daughters told us she was a nice person, but we don't align with her politically and ... because she's pro-choice, we said we should donate her money to a pro-life [cause]."" 
 Translated sentence: "“我们的女儿认为（沃伦）很好，”特朗普的支持者、其中一位女孩的父亲丹·米歇尔斯告诉《华盛顿自由灯塔》，“她过来告诉我们，我们应该投她的票。我们的女儿告诉我们，她是个好人，但我们在政治上不支持她，而且… …因为她支持选择，我们说我们应该把她的钱捐给支持生命的事业。”"

Original sentence: "In Lausanne, Switzerland, where hundreds of climate strike organizers gatheredin August planning for this week's events, thousands of people marched through the city, according to local reports." 
 Translated sentence: "据当地报道，在瑞士洛桑，数百名气候罢工组织者8月份聚集在那里，计划本周的活动，数千人在该市游行。"

Original sentence: "But the austere kingdom, which forbids alcohol and has a strict social code, is seen by many as a hard sell for tourists." 
 Translated sentence: "但是 ， 严格的王国 ， 禁止酒精 ， 并有严格的社会规范 ， 许多人认为这对游客来说是一个艰难的买卖。"

Original sentence: "Oxford Crown Court heard Clifton had been drinking mixers at the Fat Fox pub in Watlington, Oxfordshire, shortly before the assault in March last year." 
 Translated sentence: "牛津皇冠法院听说克里夫顿在牛津郡沃特灵顿的肥福克斯酒吧喝酒, 就在去年3月的攻击前不久."

Original sentence: "Abstract: A part from the price correction which is natural in speculation, the current round of digital currency tumble has also to do with the 'sworn enemy'—regulation." 
 Translated sentence: "文摘: 从投机中自然的价格调整的一部分, 当前的数字货币暴跌也与 "死敌"--监管有关。"

Original sentence: ""We have determined the cause of the problem. We are very sorry this occurred, and we have contacted the family to discuss the situation with them," the health insurer said." 
 Translated sentence: "这位健康保险公司说：“我们已经确定了问题的原因。对此事我们感到非常抱歉，我们已经与家人联系，与他们讨论这种情况。”"

Original sentence: "US theater chain bans dressing up for "Joker" screenings over fears of another shooting" 
 Translated sentence: "由于担心再次发生枪击事件，美国连锁影院禁止在“小丑”放映时穿着打扮"

Original sentence: "Experts for both sides agreed that some women seeking abortions are uncertain, and some women who go through with an abortion later regret their decision. But they differed on whether those constituted a large or small percentage of the women seeking abortions. The experts also disagreed on whether Tennessee's 48-hour waiting period would make any difference for those women." 
 Translated sentence: "双方的专家一致认为，一些寻求堕胎的妇女并不确定，一些堕胎的妇女后来对自己的决定感到遗憾，但他们对这些妇女在寻求堕胎的妇女中占很大比例还是很小的比例存在分歧，专家们还不同意田纳西州48小时的等待期是否会对这些妇女产生任何影响。"

Original sentence: "The new law, which takes effect Jan. 1, will allow police to use deadly force only when "necessary" to defend against an imminent threat of death or serious injury to officers or bystanders." 
 Translated sentence: "新 法 律 将 于 1 月 1 日 生 效 ， 将 允 许 警 察 只 有 在 “ 必 要 ” 时 才 使 用 致 命 武 力 ， 以 抵 御 警 察 或 旁 观 者 面 临 的 迫 在 眉 睫 的 死 亡 或 重 伤 威 胁 。"

Original sentence: "A Prison Service spokeswoman said: "HMP Wandsworth has increased security at the gate and is operating extra identity checks as a result of a security incident. It would be inappropriate to comment further while a police investigation is ongoing."" 
 Translated sentence: "狱政署发言人说：“由于一起安全事件，HMP Wandsworth已经加强了大门的安全，并正在进行额外的身份检查。在警方正在进行调查的时候，进一步发表评论是不合适的。”"

Original sentence: "In a December 2018 report the Energy Information Administration said it expected the United States" LNG export capacity to double by the end of this year to 8.9 billion cu ft daily. This will make the US the third-largest exporter of LNG in terms of capacity after Qatar and Australia. By 2030, US LNG exports are estimated to reach 17 billion cu ft daily, from some 3 billion cu ft at the start of 2019." 
 Translated sentence: "能源情报署在2018年12月的一份报告中表示，预计美国的液化天然气出口能力到今年年底将翻一番，达到每天89亿立方英尺。这将使美国成为仅次于卡塔尔和澳大利亚的第三大液化天然气出口国。到2030年，美国液化天然气出口量预计将从2019年初的约30亿立方英尺增至每天170亿立方英尺。"

Original sentence: "We decided to publish limited information about the whistle-blower - including the fact that he works for a nonpolitical agency and that his complaint is based on an intimate knowledge and understanding of the White House - because we wanted to provide information to readers that allows them to make their own judgments about whether or not he is credible." 
 Translated sentence: "我们决定公布有关举报人的有限信息 — — 包括他为一个非政治机构工作的事实 ， 以及他的申诉是基于对白宫的亲密知识和理解 — — 因为我们想向读者提供信息 ， 使他们能够就他是否可信做出自己的判断。"

Original sentence: "According to the forecast of Ministry of Trade and Economic Development, the country's economic growth will reach 7%, while the country's inflation is basically above this level." 
 Translated sentence: "根据预测的部贸易和经济发展，该国的经济增长将达到7%，而该国的通货膨胀基本上是高于这一水平。"

Original sentence: ""There's been a big bearish risk from a thaw in the US Iran situation for some time and this will put a remarkable amount of oil back onto the market immediately if it were to occur," said John Kilduff of Again Capital." 
 Translated sentence: "Again Capital的约翰·基尔达夫说：“一段时间以来，美国局势的解冻一直存在巨大的看跌风险，这将使大量石油立即回市。”"

Original sentence: "The head of the regional administration said Friday the fire was extinguished Thursday night after nearly 24 hours. Firefighters are still on the scene." 
 Translated sentence: "地区行政长官说,周五晚上,消防队员仍在现场,近24小时后,周四晚上灭火。"

Original sentence: "Easy use" 
 Translated sentence: "使用方便。"

Original sentence: "But with the work we've been doing, focussing on the customers needs, not our own, I think you're seeing a lot of change." 
 Translated sentence: "但在我们做的工作中 ， 专注于客户需要 ， 而不是自己 ， 我认为你会看到很多变化。"

Original sentence: "The government has compulsorily retired 15 more tax officers in the fourth tranche of its crackdown on errant officials accused of corruption and other malpractices." 
 Translated sentence: "在打击被控腐败和其他渎职行为的错误官员的第四阶段，政府强制又退休了15名税务官员。"

Original sentence: "Federal authorities declined to pursue civil rights charges Thursday against Sacramento police officers who fatally shot an unarmed black man, a killing that sparked protests and spurred changes to a state law governing when authorities can use deadly force." 
 Translated sentence: "联邦当局周四拒绝对萨克拉门托警察提出民权指控，萨克拉门托警察开枪打死了一名手无寸铁的黑人男子，这起杀人事件引发了抗议，并促使修改了关于当局何时可以使用致命武力的州法律。"

Original sentence: "Zhang Huizhen is considered as a late bloomer. She regrets about not winning the last session of the London Olympic Games tickets before, but now she proudly stands on the top of the Rio Olympic podium." 
 Translated sentence: "张先生被认为是一个迟到的火焰，她对于没有赢得最后一次伦敦奥运会票的结果感到遗憾，但现在她骄傲地站在里约奥运会的顶端。"

Original sentence: "When Sen. Elizabeth Warren (D., Mass.) purchased drinks from two girls running a lemonade stand in August, she may not have been aware that her $10 purchase would be donated to a pro-life charity." 
 Translated sentence: "当Sen. Elizabeth Warren(Mass.)在8月从两个女孩那里购买饮料时,她可能不知道她购买的10美元会捐给一个亲人慈善机构。"

Original sentence: "A participant holds a drawing depicting Swedish environmental activist Greta Thunberg during a protest march to call for action against climate change, in The Hague, Netherlands September 27, 2019. REUTERS/Piroschka van de Wouw" 
 Translated sentence: "2019年9月27日，在荷兰海牙，一名与会者拿着一幅描绘瑞典环保活动家格雷塔·通伯格（Greta Thunberg）的画，抗议呼吁采取行动应对气候变化。鲁特斯/皮罗施卡·范德沃"

Original sentence: "His lawyer, Sardar Mehmood, told AFP the court in the eastern city of Multan had found his client guilty and sentenced him to life imprisonment, in a long-awaited verdict." 
 Translated sentence: "他的律师Sardar Mehmood告诉菲律宾武装部队,在等待已久的判决中,苏丹东部市的法院判定他的当事人有罪,判处他终身监禁。"

Original sentence: "Man pleads guilty in kidnap, torture plot of plastic surgeon" 
 Translated sentence: "男 子 在 绑 架 、 折 磨 整 形 外 科 医 生 的 阴 谋 中 认 罪"

Original sentence: "The School Education and Higher Education department will organise seminars highlighting Vidaysagar's life and work in schools and colleges during a year-long programme, Mr Chatterjee said." 
 Translated sentence: "查特吉表示，学校教育和高等教育部将在为期一年的课程中组织研讨会，重点介绍维代萨加尔在学校和大学的生活和工作。"

Original sentence: "May cause liver damage - Per studies, too much coumarin can also be responsible for liver toxicity and damage. This is according to several studies made on the effects of too much coumarin in our bodies."
